The paper deals with optimization of data transmission in wireless fading channels with energy harvesting nodes, which involves information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), control systems (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.MA), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper discusses offline and online policies for optimizing transmission completion time and throughput, which are relevant to these sub-categories.
